  "instruction": "Condense to a single logarithm: log_{base}({p}) + log_{base}({q}).",
  "params": {
    "base": {
      "type": "choice",
      "choices": [
        2,
        3,
        10
      ]
    },
    "exp_p": {
      "type": "int",
      "min": 1,
      "max": 3
    },
    "exp_q": {
      "type": "int",
      "min": 1,
      "max": 3
    }
  },
  "answer_expr": "logprop",
  "steps": [
    "Apply the product rule: log_b(A) + log_b(B) = log_b(A*B).",
    "log_{base}({p}) + log_{base}({q}) = log_{base}({p} * {q}) = log_{base}({pq}).",
    "Since {base}^{answer_logprop} = {pq}, the result simplifies to {answer_logprop}."
  ],
